fr.univrennes1.cri.jtacl.core.network
Class Route<T>

java.lang.Object
  fr.univrennes1.cri.jtacl.core.network.Route<T>
Type Parameters:
T - Type of the link.
public class Route<T>
extends java.lang.Object

This class describes a route.
A route is composed by a IPNet IP prefix, the IPNet IP address of the next hop, and a metric that could be use to sort routes. A route is associated to a link describing the outgoing link for this route.

Author:
Patrick Lamaiziere
